{"tid":1369122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〔牧師嘅啟發〕我係不折不扣嘅和理非，聽日我絕對會出嚟。","createTime":"2019-07-26T15:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:41:57.000Z","uid":191290,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2d16f0be375aae8d357fa09fba24940b5091f90c","tid":1369122,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"因為<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">人多就可以保護到所有人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g9B9Mp8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg9B9Mp8.gif&h=1720ac45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武、和理非同行，多你一個真係多好多！<br />\n當你淆底諗緊縮唔縮沙，不如諗下，一路以嚟我哋之間嘅互信，係令我哋可以走到呢度嘅原因！<br />\n<br />\n因為相信大家，就算驚都好，從來都唔會由得手足置身危險。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">所以聽日，我哋得2個女仔都會入去！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">山長水遠深入敵陣都無懼，係因為大家都係值得信任嘅人！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位，好好休息，聽日見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"aef240d70504df211f561b99ea8fe5a9d83147dd","tid":1369122,"uid":191290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"淆底嘅入嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e00e50cc88908f9e8929cde684e4445e6d90f7d","tid":1369122,"uid":191290,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">仲有，今次政府reject遊行申請，某程度係試緊水溫。聽日嘅人數，係反映咗我哋抗爭到底嘅決心。如果人少，政府就會開始有位入，知道我哋驚啲咩，以後照板煮碗！</span></span>"},{"pid":"6002e474b19b292231766c376138dd998e852199","tid":1369122,"uid":191290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:51:38.000Z","msg":"所以我哋更加唔可以淆！<br />\n要話畀班仆街聽，遊行本身就係我哋應有嘅權利，無論佢哋不反對定反對！<br />\n話事嘅係民意，唔係班閪狗！"},{"pid":"615b44564b7443f622e975003b94d696e67a12f4","tid":1369122,"uid":260428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"大家都眼目近日元朗新聞<br />\n咁都可以指麇為那 癲倒是非<br />\n<br />\n大家自問一下，<br />\n做下心理功課，諗下應對，<br />\n以免入村變入侵，又有人保家衛國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 有人沖入，你跟唔跟<br />\n2. 村入面有人撩你，你沖唔沖<br />\n3. 有人打完手足，龜入村，你沖唔沖<br />\n4. 有人捉左手足入村，救唔救！<br />\n5. 警察三面圍迫，焗你入村<br />\n6. 圍村要交人，圍幾耐，點進行下一步<br />\n7. 如果非法遊行被捉，點做？<br />\n<br />\n一定要記者<br />\n拍片紀錄係最強大武器<br />\n<br />\n一定要先禮後兵<br />\n有聲公講清楚發生咩事，唔要得口號。<br />\n就算手捉被人捉左入村！"},{"pid":"143b5592505a4d802ddb98becbc31e3cce5f2b35","tid":1369122,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:53:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更 加 唔 係 班 低 智 黑 社 會</span>"},{"pid":"fa62c5566f24541013de3c0146cfe5283675cf84","tid":1369122,"uid":209153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:54:57.000Z","msg":"到時你地可以同附近啲女仔組團 人多冇咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1808c56902037e13dedd2773e1888bfb5a3c8ab","tid":1369122,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa62c5566f24541013de3c0146cfe5283675cf84","tid":1369122,"uid":209153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:54:57.000Z","msg":"到時你地可以同附近啲女仔組團 人多冇咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:59:14.000Z","msg":"會即場組多啲人啊<br />\nFull gear + 行山杖，呢個星期仲練咗啲防衛術，希望保護到自己同身邊嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c603ab5811199942c7e82924cecd67e6c00dc90","tid":1369122,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:41:57.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"}]}